WEBVTT

00:06:28.412 --> 00:06:32.204
Now, suicide is not an unusual event

00:06:32.228 --> 00:06:34.145
in the world of mental health.

00:06:35.101 --> 00:06:37.724
But there was something
about Erica's death

00:06:37.748 --> 00:06:40.894
that struck me at the core
of my very being.

00:06:42.367 --> 00:06:45.182
That statement from Erica's mother:

00:06:45.766 --> 00:06:50.198
"We didn't have 15 dollars bus fare
to come to you,"

00:06:51.103 --> 00:06:52.768
made me realize

00:06:53.784 --> 00:06:55.925
that it just wasn't going to work,

00:06:55.949 --> 00:06:58.457
me expecting people to come to me.

00:06:58.813 --> 00:07:02.546
And I got into this state
of soul-searching,